query:
SELECT MIN(n.name) AS of_person, MIN(t.title) AS biography_movie
 FROM aka_name AS an,
 cast_info AS ci,
 info_type AS it,
 link_type AS lt,
 movie_link AS ml,
 name AS n,
 person_info AS pi,
 title AS t
 WHERE n.id = an.person_id
 AND n.id = pi.person_id
 AND ci.person_id = n.id
 AND t.id = ci.movie_id
 AND ml.linked_movie_id = t.id
 AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
 AND it.id = pi.info_type_id
 AND pi.person_id = an.person_id
 AND pi.person_id = ci.person_id
 AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
 AND ci.movie_id = ml.linked_movie_id
 AND an.name LIKE '%a%'
 AND it.info = 'mini biography'
 AND lt.link = 'features'
 AND (n.gender = 'm' OR (n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%t%'))
 AND pi.note = 'Jim Beaver <jumblejim@prodigy.net>';

query:
SELECT MIN(n.name) AS of_person, MIN(t.title) AS biography_movie
 FROM aka_name AS an,
 cast_info AS ci,
 info_type AS it,
 link_type AS lt,
 movie_link AS ml,
 name AS n,
 person_info AS pi,
 title AS t
 WHERE n.id = an.person_id
 AND n.id = pi.person_id
 AND ci.person_id = n.id
 AND t.id = ci.movie_id
 AND ml.linked_movie_id = t.id
 AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
 AND it.id = pi.info_type_id
 AND pi.person_id = an.person_id
 AND pi.person_id = ci.person_id
 AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
 AND ci.movie_id = ml.linked_movie_id
 AND an.name LIKE '%,%'
 AND it.info = 'mini biography'
 AND lt.link = 'edited from'
 AND (n.gender = 'm' OR (n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%b%'))
 AND pi.note = 'Jon C. Hopwood';
